name: Entersms
body:
EnterSMS (Enterprise School Management System)

EnterSMS is an enterprise standard open-source school management system. Feel free to contribute to it.
This is highly influenced by Fedena(https://github.com/projectfedena/fedena/). This is a hobby project and this software come with absolutely no warranty.
